SUMMARY:Spring 2027 1-Year B'nai Mitzvah Family Meeting
DESCRIPTION:This meeting will give both students and parents the opportunity to see their Torah portions in English for the first time\, gain insight into the B’nai Mitzvah preparation process\, and get answers to many of your questions. \nThis meeting is only for families with a simcha between February and June 2027. \nRegister here to receive the Zoom link.
URL:https://nertamid.org/event/spring-2027-1-year-bnai-mitzvah-family-meeting/
CATEGORIES:General
END:VEVENT
